description: State leaders argue that the cargo ship was not fit to sail on March 26, and its owner, Grace Ocean Private Limited, and manager, Synergy Marine Group, failed to take precautions to prevent the crash.
title: The state of Maryland sues Dali ship owner and manager over the Key Bridge collapse

description: Since its re-release earlier this month, Travis Scott's album Days Before Rodeo has been bouncing up and down the charts, finally landing at number one.
title: Travis Scott finally soars to No. 1 on the strength of vinyl

description: Rooney's fourth novel is a story about learning to accept loss. And though it has its share of grief and strife, it's happier and less disturbing than Normal People and Beautiful World, Where Are You.
title: 'Intermezzo' is Sally Rooney's most moving novel yet
